{"sha": "5b9bac2ab62063229c419909f89a41890c57f78f", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOjViOWJhYzJhYjYyMDYzMjI5YzQxOTkwOWY4OWE0MTg5MGM1N2Y3OGY=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "\u00d6mer Sinan A\u011facan", "email": "omeragacan@gmail.com", "date": "2021-03-21T14:29:21Z"}, "committer": {"name": "\u00d6mer Sinan A\u011facan", "email": "omeragacan@gmail.com", "date": "2021-03-27T10:06:36Z"}, "message": "format macro argument parsing fix\n\nWhen the character next to `{}` is \"shifted\" (when mapping a byte index\nin the format string to span) we should avoid shifting the span end\nindex, so first map the index of `}` to span, then bump the span,\ninstead of first mapping the next byte index to a span (which causes\nbumping the end span too much).\n\nRegression test added.\n\nFixes #83344", "tree": {"sha": "c14ccada7ceaaf8f6fd052194fb0c3a79f339f62", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/c14ccada7ceaaf8f6fd052194fb0c3a79f339f62"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/5b9bac2ab62063229c419909f89a41890c57f78f", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/5b9bac2ab62063229c419909f89a41890c57f78f", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/5b9bac2ab62063229c419909f89a41890c57f78f", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/5b9bac2ab62063229c419909f89a41890c57f78f/comments", "author": {"login": "osa1", "id": 448274, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ0ODI3NA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/448274?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/osa1", "html_url": "https://github.com/osa1", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/osa1/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/osa1/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/osa1/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/us